<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>49</hymn_number>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A tu le atu khua a mui, Na luhnak lam kha a har ko, Ngaihchiatnak atu
 le atu, Nangmah thlarau kha a huh ko,

[C1]
   Jesuh sinah ka tlikter tuah, (tlikter tuah) Keimah nakin a cung
   Jesuh kha, (Jesuh kha) Jesuh sinah ka tlikter tuah, (tlikter tuah) Keimah
   nakin a cung Jesuh kha.

[V2]
 Atu le a tu ni a sau, Voi tampi kehlan a rit ko, Vawlei nun lam ka kal
 lio ah, Jesuh thladem kha a dai ko,

[C2]
   Jesuh sinah ka tlikter tuah, (tlikter tuah) Keimah nakin a cung
   Jesuh kha, (Jesuh kha) Jesuh sinah ka tlikter tuah, (tlikter tuah) Keimah
   nakin a cung Jesuh kha.

[V3]
 Jesuh pawngah um ko u si, Kan that le kan chiat ah siseh, Chuk le cho
 kan zuan ah si seh, Khuamui lak kan kal ah siseh.

[C3]
   Jesuh sinah ka tlikter tuah, (tlikter tuah) Keimah nakin a cung
   Jesuh kha, (Jesuh kha) Jesuh sinah ka tlikter tuah, (tlikter tuah) Keimah
   nakin a cung Jesuh kha.</lyrics>
<title>KEIMAH NAK SANG DEUHMI LUNGPI CH49</title>
</song>